title: Commodore Amiga - Applications - ADF (TOSEC 20100813)
description:
This is my first torrent so be gentle guys.

I had trouble finding applications for my newly downloaded Amiga emulator and the other torrents here on the Bay are (were on the time of upload) either fakes or dead.

I found these programs on the English Amiga Board (eab.abime.net) and put them into a convenient package for you. If I understand it correctly these programs are abandonware (the copyright holders rarely cares or don't exist anymore) but since the typical ownership of a copyright extends for FIFTY years this software would be lost or irrelevant by then. I hope through emulators and the more and more powerful handheld devices some of these vintage applications will again be of use to people. Enjoy!

To unpack the file you will need 7z and either an emulator or another program on your Amiga to run or uncompress the ADF-files.
